  "description": "Alterations including erection of mansard roof extension to main rear roof; erection of extension above part of two storey back addition and formation of rear roof terrace with 1.7m high obscured glazed screening.",
  "lapsed_date": "26/04/2025",
  "lpa_app_no": "2022/0941",
